16
00:02:06,670 --> 00:02:08,350
(Liang)
(bertukar daripada pertahanan kepada menyerang)

17
00:02:08,670 --> 00:02:10,900
(dan akhirnya berhenti seketika.)

18
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:15,860
Meng.

19
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:18,300
Di manakah Jeneral?

20
00:02:18,860 --> 00:02:20,270
Dia berkata dia akan kembali ke Nandu.

21
00:02:20,740 --> 00:02:21,853
Jadi, dia tidak akan pergi dengan kita.

22
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:25,650
Meng, mari kita pergi sekarang.

23
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:27,420
Jeneral dan Xiaoxiao

24
00:02:27,420 --> 00:02:28,580
akan menjaga diri mereka sendiri.

25
00:02:30,616 --> 00:02:31,745
Jeneral akan berjumpa

26
00:02:31,756 --> 00:02:32,430
beberapa kawan.

27
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:33,583
Kita jumpa lagi di Nandu.

28
00:02:35,140 --> 00:02:35,980
Dalam kes itu,

29
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:37,070
sebaik sahaja kami sampai di Nandu,

30
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:38,550
Saya akan minum

31
00:02:38,730 --> 00:02:39,783
dengan beberapa kawan lama juga.

32
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,420
Terima kasih atas jemputan.

33
00:02:41,580 --> 00:02:42,620
Saya akan ke sana tepat pada masanya.

34
00:02:44,550 --> 00:02:45,830
Bagi kapasiti minum anda,

35
00:02:47,110 --> 00:02:48,300
awak patut duduk dengan Chenying.

36
00:02:49,223 --> 00:02:50,956
- Saya tidak boleh minum.
- Berbanding dengan kali terakhir,

37
00:02:50,967 --> 00:02:51,950
Saya boleh melakukan lebih baik sekarang.

38
00:02:53,350 --> 00:02:54,670
Kemudian saya akan menantikannya.

39
00:02:59,340 --> 00:03:01,380
(Liang)

40
00:03:11,830 --> 00:03:12,670
Simu.

41
00:03:16,990 --> 00:03:17,830
makanlah.

42
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:25,600
Adakah anda tidak akan bertanya apa itu?

43
00:03:27,270 --> 00:03:28,110
Anda tidak akan membahayakan saya.

44
00:03:29,510 --> 00:03:30,350
Jika anda bermaksud mencederakan saya,

45
00:03:30,633 --> 00:03:31,826
tiada apa yang boleh saya lakukan.

46
00:03:36,110 --> 00:03:36,950
Apa yang anda telan

47
00:03:37,270 --> 00:03:38,740
ialah Tanglung Roh dalam gula.

48
00:03:40,900 --> 00:03:41,740
Tanglung Roh?

49
00:03:41,751 --> 00:03:43,017
Satu artifak Dunia Roh.

50
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:44,670
Dengan itu, kuasa semangat seseorang

51
00:03:44,670 --> 00:03:45,670
boleh tumbuh lebih sepuluh kali ganda.

52
00:03:46,140 --> 00:03:47,460
Ia mewakili Yang Berdaulat.

53
00:03:47,950 --> 00:03:49,700
Semua roh sangat mendambakannya,

54
00:03:49,830 --> 00:03:51,390
masing-masing terdesak nak tuntut dulu.

55
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:53,180
Dan kini ia berada di dalam diri anda.

56
00:04:22,790 --> 00:04:23,670
Simu,

57
00:04:26,500 --> 00:04:27,693
macam ni lah semangat.

58
00:04:46,380 --> 00:04:47,260
Foxy,

59
00:04:48,990 --> 00:04:50,820
selamat datang ke dunia roh.

60
00:05:20,710 --> 00:05:21,550
Mulai sekarang,

61
00:05:22,110 --> 00:05:23,670
anda boleh menggunakan kuasa Deliverance

62
00:05:23,990 --> 00:05:25,180
untuk membangkitkan Tanglung Roh.

63
00:05:29,180 --> 00:05:30,566
Anda takut bahawa selepas pertukaran,

64
00:05:30,666 --> 00:05:32,239
anda akan menjadi manusia
tanpa kuasa roh,

65
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:33,380
jadi awak

66
00:05:33,380 --> 00:05:34,670
menjadikan saya semangat untuk melindungi awak.

67
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:36,350
Saya rasa begitu.

68
00:05:37,790 --> 00:05:38,630
Sudah tentu,

69
00:05:39,150 --> 00:05:39,990
Saya tidak akan mengecewakan awak.

70
00:06:05,940 --> 00:06:06,780
awak buat apa?

71
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:22,406
Kelopak seperti jed basah dengan embun
mengeluarkan bunga yang harum.

72
00:06:22,740 --> 00:06:24,500
Sebelum musim bunga, mereka menunggu masa jayanya.

73
00:06:25,710 --> 00:06:28,460
Aroma mereka membuatkan jiwa terpesona.

74
00:06:32,620 --> 00:06:34,350
Angin yang wangi
memikat hati orang yang lalu lalang.

75
00:06:36,076 --> 00:06:37,445
Jadi, perkara dalam buku ayah saya

76
00:06:37,456 --> 00:06:38,020
semuanya benar.

77
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:42,190
Simu,

78
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:46,260
selamat kembali ke dunia manusia.

79
00:06:50,670 --> 00:06:54,380
♪Jatuh seperti salji♪

80
00:06:54,850 --> 00:06:58,330
♪Kegembiraan dan kesedihan dunia fana♪

81
00:06:58,330 --> 00:07:02,210
♪Dihanyutkan oleh cahaya siang♪

82
00:07:02,620 --> 00:07:06,420
♪Bentuk dan warna alam fana♪

83
00:07:06,690 --> 00:07:09,360
♪Berlama-lama sekejap♪

84
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:13,840
♪Pernah tersentuh air mata ketawa♪

85
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:17,230
♪Jika saya boleh hidup sederhana♪

86
00:07:17,230 --> 00:07:18,070
♪Sekali♪

87
00:07:18,070 --> 00:07:23,150
♪Saya akan menjadi tetamu dalam mimpi yang indah♪

88
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:28,740
♪Subuh dan senja terbit dan terbenam♪

89
00:07:29,010 --> 00:07:32,540
♪Rindu bertemu, namun berpisah dengan takdir♪

90
00:07:33,050 --> 00:07:36,660
♪Izinkan saya merayau♪

91
00:07:36,660 --> 00:07:40,300
♪Terang dan gelap, tanpa berpatah balik♪

92
00:07:40,710 --> 00:07:44,110
♪Merayau ke pantai lain
dengan tanglung♪

93
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:48,240
♪Diiringi keabadian♪

94
00:07:48,450 --> 00:07:51,140
♪Ketika semua perkara berputar dan mengalir♪

95
00:07:51,260 --> 00:07:57,170
♪Sama ada saya tinggal atau pergi, saya keseorangan♪

96
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:01,020
Simu.

97
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:03,460
Simu.

98
00:08:11,530 --> 00:08:14,900
♪Jatuh seperti salji♪

99
00:08:17,110 --> 00:08:18,110
Apakah bau itu?

100
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:22,350
Ini ialah

101
00:08:24,790 --> 00:08:25,630
gaharu,

102
00:08:27,260 --> 00:08:28,100
ambar,

103
00:08:30,350 --> 00:08:31,190
storax,

104
00:08:32,380 --> 00:08:33,230
daun pudina,

105
00:08:33,230 --> 00:08:34,070
Bletilla,

106
00:08:34,380 --> 00:08:35,220
dan benzoin.

107
00:08:37,310 --> 00:08:38,336
Kakak saya suka wangian.

108
00:08:38,710 --> 00:08:39,550
Dia menggunakan wangian

109
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:41,470
untuk mewangi

110
00:08:41,470 --> 00:08:42,310
jubah harian saya.

111
00:08:43,620 --> 00:08:44,460
Gaharu,

112
00:08:46,020 --> 00:08:46,860
ambar,

113
00:08:47,470 --> 00:08:48,350
storax,

114
00:08:49,380 --> 00:08:51,430
daun pudina, Bletilla,

115
00:08:52,380 --> 00:08:53,260
dan benzoin.

116
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:59,030
♪Terang dan gelap, tanpa berpatah balik♪

117
00:08:59,230 --> 00:09:00,070
Ia berbau harum.

118
00:09:00,070 --> 00:09:02,990
♪Merayau ke pantai lain
dengan tanglung♪

119
00:09:03,060 --> 00:09:07,130
♪Diiringi keabadian♪

120
00:09:07,130 --> 00:09:09,710
♪Ketika semua perkara berputar dan mengalir♪

121
00:09:09,980 --> 00:09:13,140
♪Sama ada saya tinggal atau pergi, saya keseorangan♪

122
00:09:13,190 --> 00:09:14,500
Tentera telah kembali berehat.

123
00:09:15,830 --> 00:09:16,950
Kebetulan saya juga bebas.

124
00:09:17,990 --> 00:09:18,830
Bagaimana pula saya mengembara

125
00:09:19,540 --> 00:09:20,540
dengan awak sekejap?

126
00:09:28,620 --> 00:09:29,710
Jom ikut saya ke Youzhou

127
00:09:29,900 --> 00:09:31,190
untuk berjumpa kawan lama.

128
00:09:32,540 --> 00:09:33,540
Saya kebetulan tahu

129
00:09:33,540 --> 00:09:34,710
pembuat wangian berbakat

130
00:09:35,710 --> 00:09:36,550
di Youzhou.

131
00:09:36,990 --> 00:09:37,830
Adakah anda mahu belajar

132
00:09:38,140 --> 00:09:38,980
membuat wangian?

133
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:40,660
Jika anda lakukan,

134
00:09:41,530 --> 00:09:42,380
mulakan dengan mengadun

135
00:09:42,380 --> 00:09:43,220
bau pada saya.

136
00:09:44,100 --> 00:09:44,950
Kenapa mesti

137
00:09:44,950 --> 00:09:46,070
bau pada awak?

138
00:09:46,070 --> 00:09:48,680
♪Lampu bersendirian bersinar di pantai lain♪

139
00:09:48,710 --> 00:09:50,190
Sebab awak suka.

140
00:09:51,783 --> 00:09:52,670
Berapa lama masa yang diperlukan?

141
00:09:54,070 --> 00:09:54,910
Sehingga hari

142
00:09:56,710 --> 00:09:58,070
masa kita sudah tamat.

143
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:00,860
Bagaimana jika

144
00:10:01,430 --> 00:10:02,310
Saya gagal ketika itu?

145
00:10:04,656 --> 00:10:05,950
Saya belum memilih taruhan lagi.

146
00:10:06,263 --> 00:10:07,220
Awak boleh berhutang dengan saya buat masa ini.

147
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:12,990
Jangan terlalu yakin anda akan menang.

148
00:10:18,710 --> 00:10:20,190
Sup kambing mereka sangat baik.

149
00:10:21,070 --> 00:10:21,990
Anda sepatutnya mempunyai mangkuk.

150
00:10:21,990 --> 00:10:23,020
Kemudian saya mesti mencuba beberapa.

151
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:34,860
(Bandar Fujian, Youzhou)

152
00:10:36,260 --> 00:10:37,100
Yili'er,

153
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:38,990
masih tiada kemajuan

154
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:40,190
atas perintah diraja.

155
00:10:41,350 --> 00:10:42,260
Adakah anda tidak mahu

156
00:10:42,260 --> 00:10:43,430
untuk berkhidmat kepada diraja lagi?

157
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:47,990
Ini menyangkut perang dengan Great Liang.

158
00:10:48,590 --> 00:10:49,860
Mahkamah Diraja memerlukan anda

159
00:10:49,860 --> 00:10:51,900
untuk mencari lombong emas baru
untuk gaji tentera.

160
00:10:52,420 --> 00:10:54,060
(Yili'er, saudagar Youzhou)
Dalam seminggu,

161
00:10:54,070 --> 00:10:54,910
kami akan datang lagi.

162
00:10:55,590 --> 00:10:56,609
Saya hanya berharap pada masa itu,

163
00:10:56,780 --> 00:10:57,760
anda boleh berikan kami

164
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:58,830
jawapan yang jelas

165
00:10:59,230 --> 00:11:01,780
dan meringankan beban Mahkamah Diraja.

166
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:04,070
ya.

167
00:11:04,780 --> 00:11:07,260
Saya tidak akan gagalkan Mahkamah Diraja.

168
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:28,380
(Gerbang Selatan)

169
00:11:56,350 --> 00:11:57,380
Anak saya akan menyukainya.

170
00:11:57,380 --> 00:11:58,220
Youzhou telah berkembang

171
00:11:59,190 --> 00:12:00,350
begitu makmur.

172
00:12:01,430 --> 00:12:02,270
Pertahanan ketat,

173
00:12:02,990 --> 00:12:03,830
jelapang penuh.

174
00:12:05,140 --> 00:12:06,720
Nasib baik, kami tidak menyerang Youzhou dahulu.

175
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:14,900
(Pewangi)

176
00:12:14,900 --> 00:12:15,830
selamat tinggal.

177
00:12:16,110 --> 00:12:17,140
terima kasih.

178
00:12:19,190 --> 00:12:20,230
Cik, lihat sekeliling.

179
00:12:20,470 --> 00:12:22,070
Kami mempunyai bola wangian segar hari ini.

180
00:12:25,900 --> 00:12:26,780
Bau yang harum.

181
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:28,260
Ini dia.

182
00:12:29,310 --> 00:12:30,196
Jom pilih yang ini.

183
00:12:35,710 --> 00:12:36,550
Cik,

184
00:12:36,830 --> 00:12:37,860
adakah anda Liu Ruyu?

185
00:12:47,230 --> 00:12:48,830
Dari mana datangnya sachet ini?

186
00:12:54,230 --> 00:12:55,190
Pemiliknya berkata

187
00:12:55,540 --> 00:12:57,070
anda akan faham selepas surat ini.

188
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:03,580
(Kepada Liu Ruyu)

189
00:13:03,580 --> 00:13:05,180
(Kawan saya minat wangian.)

190
00:13:05,180 --> 00:13:06,715
(Anda pakar. Tolong bimbing dia.)

191
00:13:06,726 --> 00:13:07,700
(Duan Shunxi)

192
00:13:09,610 --> 00:13:10,470
Anak nakal!

193
00:13:10,470 --> 00:13:11,500
Berhenti berlari jika anda berani!

194
00:13:15,020 --> 00:13:16,140
Berhenti!

195
00:13:21,540 --> 00:13:22,380
Awak...

196
00:13:29,310 --> 00:13:30,190
Saya baru beli

197
00:13:30,190 --> 00:13:31,590
drum pelet ini untuk anda.

198
00:13:33,500 --> 00:13:34,470
Adakah anda suka?

199
00:13:34,770 --> 00:13:35,620
saya buat.

200
00:13:35,620 --> 00:13:37,140
Terima kasih, Ibu.

201
00:13:37,590 --> 00:13:38,900
perempuan baik.

202
00:13:39,230 --> 00:13:40,070
Ibu,

203
00:13:40,260 --> 00:13:41,660
saya lapar.

204
00:13:41,770 --> 00:13:42,620
Baiklah.

205
00:13:42,620 --> 00:13:43,710
Saya akan pulang dan membuat

206
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:44,700
beberapa kebaikan untuk anda.

207
00:13:45,070 --> 00:13:46,470
Kuasa saya telah berkembang terlalu banyak.

208
00:13:46,710 --> 00:13:47,620
Saya hilang kawalan.

209
00:13:50,190 --> 00:13:51,030
siapa awak

210
00:13:51,230 --> 00:13:52,350
Mengapa membunuh roh di sini?

211
00:13:54,110 --> 00:13:54,950
saya minta maaf.

212
00:13:55,230 --> 00:13:56,070
Saya tidak sengaja.

213
00:14:01,350 --> 00:14:02,190
Lupakan saja.

214
00:14:02,540 --> 00:14:04,110
Ia adalah roh yang ditandai untuk kematian.

215
00:14:04,590 --> 00:14:06,430
Saya hanya akan melaporkan apa yang berlaku.

216
00:14:07,740 --> 00:14:08,580
Namun,

217
00:14:08,780 --> 00:14:09,830
bagaimana anda menguruskan

218
00:14:10,260 --> 00:14:11,110
dengan badan roh

219
00:14:11,110 --> 00:14:12,350
untuk menggunakan pedang roh fana?

220
00:14:14,780 --> 00:14:15,990
Saya sudah lama hilang ingatan.

221
00:14:16,790 --> 00:14:18,020
Apabila saya sedar,

222
00:14:18,660 --> 00:14:20,110
Saya telah mempunyai pedang ini pada saya.

223
00:14:22,620 --> 00:14:23,460
Anda mesti pernah

224
00:14:23,620 --> 00:14:24,470
baru jadi semangat

225
00:14:24,620 --> 00:14:25,780
daripada Spirit Aura.

226
00:14:26,950 --> 00:14:28,350
Tidak hairanlah anda tahu begitu sedikit.

227
00:14:30,020 --> 00:14:30,860
Rakan muda,

228
00:14:31,590 --> 00:14:32,710
adakah anda membuat tangkapan?

229
00:14:34,190 --> 00:14:35,030
betul tu.

230
00:14:35,310 --> 00:14:36,900
Tetapi jangan panggil saya anak muda.

231
00:14:37,243 --> 00:14:38,732
Di Dunia Roh, pangkat tidak dinilai

232
00:14:38,743 --> 00:14:39,310
dengan penampilan.

233
00:14:39,310 --> 00:14:40,230
Saya berusia lebih 600 tahun.

234
00:14:41,710 --> 00:14:42,590
Awak nampak

235
00:14:43,350 --> 00:14:44,310
agak muda.

236
00:14:44,590 --> 00:14:46,020
Awak patut panggil saya tuan.

237
00:14:48,260 --> 00:14:49,100
saya nampak.

238
00:14:49,470 --> 00:14:50,620
Mohon pencerahan, tuan.

239
00:14:51,350 --> 00:14:52,860
Anda telah merebut semangat itu.

240
00:14:53,310 --> 00:14:54,403
Apakah kesalahan yang dia lakukan?

241
00:14:54,620 --> 00:14:55,660
Membunuh tanpa sebab

242
00:14:55,730 --> 00:14:56,936
dalam 32 Dekri Golden-wall.

243
00:14:57,620 --> 00:14:58,700
Itu adalah satu kesalahan besar.

244
00:14:59,190 --> 00:15:00,830
Saya telah memburunya selama beberapa hari dengan perintah.

245
00:15:02,260 --> 00:15:04,220
(Li Renyi)

246
00:15:05,710 --> 00:15:07,540
32 Dekri Golden-wall?

247
00:15:09,110 --> 00:15:10,190
Tolong beritahu saya tentang mereka.

248
00:15:10,753 --> 00:15:11,942
Jika tidak, saya mungkin melanggar undang-undang

249
00:15:11,953 --> 00:15:12,700
tanpa disedari.

250
00:15:13,540 --> 00:15:15,430
Kehilangan ingatan anda benar-benar menyeluruh.

